In today's age of comic book media you really need to do something different to stand out. If you can be unique you can capture the imagination of the fanbase and gain immortality. That is what Season 1 of Invincible on Amazon Prime managed to do in just 8 episodes. Based on the series written by Walking Dead creator Robert Kirkman, Invincible takes everything you know about the common origin story journey and throws a monkey wrench in it. Join us as we talk all things Mark Grayson, Omni-Man and THAT TRAIN SCENE in this spoiler-filled discussion of all things Invincible.

